  </sponsors>
  <source>Hoffmann-La Roche</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is a prospective, cross-sectional survey to be administered to real patients in
      remission from DLBCL using a 15-minute postal or online survey. The project is designed to
      describe the impact of DLBCL remission on health utility and quality of life. Data collection
      will occur over a 4-month period.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
